<h1 id="1-enable-submissions">1. Enable Submissions</h1>

<p>First, we will create a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">submit</code> template for the user to</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <ol>
      <li>submit a message in a text box</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li>
    <ol>
      <li>submit a name in a text box</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>Here, I added <strong>navigation links</strong> to submit and view messages. Then, I have <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">submit</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">view</code> template <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">extend</code> <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">base</code> using ` extends â€˜base.htmlâ€™` command.</p>

